examples.en: I ripped the poster off the wall.
The wind ripped the sail to pieces.
She was wearing ripped jeans.
examples.ru: Она была одета в рваные джинсы.

examples.en: She ripped off her mask.
Seeing his enemy, he ripped off a curse.
The buttons had been ripped off.
The curtain ripped from top to bottom
The sails ripped under the force of the wind.
She ripped the fabric in half.
He ripped the letter from my hands.
examples.ru: Он вырвал письмо у меня из рук.

examples.en: Jim ripped the cover from the book.
He ripped the page out of the magazine.
examples.ru: Он вырвал эту страницу из журнала.

examples.en: His arm was ripped to pieces by a shark.
examples.ru: Его рука была изодрана в клочья акулой.

examples.en: Impatiently, Sue ripped the letter open.
That hurricane ripped the whole village apart.
examples.ru: Этот ураган разнёс на куски целую деревню.

examples.en: Her coat ripped when it caught on the doorknob.
examples.ru: Её пальто порвалось, зацепившись за дверную ручку.

examples.en: The criminals have ripped the telephone wires out.
That dog has ripped this morning's newspaper up again!
The explosion ripped off the whole front of the restaurant.
The photographs of the unpopular leader had been ripped down.
examples.ru: Афиши с портретом непопулярного лидера были сорваны.

examples.en: I ripped out the telephone wire that ran through to his office.
examples.ru: Я вырвал телефонный провод, который шёл в его кабинет.

examples.en: He ripped open the package.
The agency really ripped us off.
Her clothes had all been ripped.
The dog ripped the pillow to shreds .
He ripped his left trouser on the fence
examples.ru: Он порвал свою левую штанину об забор / ограду.

examples.en: The sink had been ripped from the wall.
Sue ripped his photo up into tiny bits.
examples.ru: Сью разорвала его фото на маленькие кусочки.

examples.en: I expected to have my argument ripped to shreds.
examples.ru: Я думал, что мои доводы просто разорвут в мелкие клочья.

examples.en: The candidate ripped into his opponent mercilessly.
examples.ru: Кандидат безжалостно набросился на своего противника.
